this is a napt repository.
napt repositories uses:
releases / ← releases
release/ ← the release name
repo-metadata ← self explanatory
inside of it,it is like that:
[napt repository]
release=name
packages:
ryzenadj=ryzenadj_0.17.0_amd64.deb sha256=
tocafetch=tocafetch_3.1-1_amd64.deb sha256=
xpadneo=xpadneo-dkms-0.9.8_amd64.deb sha256=
nsm=nsm_2.2_amd64.deb sha256=
napt=napt-2-amd64.deb sha256=
nlc=nlc_2.2_amd64.deb sha256=
required:
{nsm};
{napt};
{nlc}
